    <subfield code="a">The Consistent Chiral Anomaly in Supersymmetric {Yang-Mills} Theories</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="246" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">THE CONSISTENT CHIRAL ANOMALY IN SUPERSYMMETRIC YANG-MILLS THEORIES</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="260" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
